		<title>Microsoft to invest $10 billion in Japan for AI and cybersecurity</title>
		<link>https://techwireasia.com/2026/04/microsoft-to-invest-10-billion-in-japan-for-ai-and-cybersecurity/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Muhammad Zulhusni]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 08:30:14 +0000</pubDate>
