		<title>Enterprise data resilience is no longer about backup. AI broke the old rules.</title>
		<link>https://techwireasia.com/2026/04/enterprise-data-resilience-ai-era-backup/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Dashveenjit Kaur]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 00:00:09 +0000</pubDate>
