		<title>Asia&#8217;s automakers are placing their Level 4 bets on NVIDIA DRIVE Hyperion</title>
		<link>https://techwireasia.com/2026/03/nvidia-drive-hyperion-asia-autonomous-vehicles-apac/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Dashveenjit Kaur]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 02:00:46 +0000</pubDate>
